<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Classification">Classification</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Indo-Aryan_languages&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Classification">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>There can be no definitive enumeration of Indo-Aryan languages because the dialects form a group of continua.
</p><p>The classification follows Masica (1991) and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kausen" title="Kausen">Kausen</a> (2006).
</p>
<div class="PieChartTemplate thumb tright" style=""><div class="thumbinner" style="width:202px">
