<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Northern_Zone">Northern Zone</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Indo-Aryan_languages&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Northern Zone">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
