<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Western_Zone">Western Zone</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Indo-Aryan_languages&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Western Zone">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>Ethnologue lists the following languages under the Western Zone that are not already covered in other subgroups:<sup id="cite_ref-12" class="reference"><a href="Old_Indic#cite_note-12">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>
