<td><span class="IPA nowrap" title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)">/<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Voiceless_bilabial_stop" title="Voiceless bilabial stop">p</a>/</span>, <span class="IPA nowrap" title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)">/<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Voiceless_dental_stop" class="mw-redirect" title="Voiceless dental stop">t̪</a>/</span>, <span class="IPA nowrap" title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)">/<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Voiceless_retroflex_stop" title="Voiceless retroflex stop">ʈ</a>/</span>, <span class="IPA nowrap" title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)">/<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Voiceless_velar_stop" title="Voiceless velar stop">k</a>/</span></td>
